snippet.title: Henchman Story - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/silkensail/henchman-story 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1449510/Henchman_Story

Henchman Story is a visual novel where you play as a beleaguered henchman working for a bumbling supervillain, and now it's live on Kickstarter! Even henchmen have bills to pay, and sometimes, even henchmen can make choices that change everything.

Trailer Edited by Andrew Moers - https://www.youtube.com/c/AndrewMoers/
Music: "Stickybee" by Josh Woodward
Fanfare for Space by Kevin MacLeod
Link: https://incompetech.filmmusic.io/song/3736-fanfare-for-space
License: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Cast:
Announcer - Carl G. Brooks
Kate - Anairis Quiñones
Dave and Chef Antonio - Anthony Sardinha
Miss Dynamo - Daphne Nitsuga
Madame Scorpion - Elissa Park
Stan and Lord Bedlam - Marc Soskin

A game by Silken Sail Entertainment. Follow us on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SilkenSail
ich.io: https://silkensail.itch.io/henchman-story
Our Website: http://www.silkensail.com
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/silken_sail/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SilkenSail
